"Change Set:		7676Kernel-dtl.232Kernel-dtl.232:Update #oopString commentKernel-dtl.226:Reference Mantis 7221: Remove some leftover VMMaker methods from base images.Remove several C code generation methods that have previously been recategorized to the VMMaker package.Kernel-ar.229:Merging Kernel-djr.228:CompiledMethod>>= seems to be broken. Attempt to fix it.MethodProperties>>analogousCodeTo: calls Pragma>>analogousCodeTo: which does not exist.Further assume when both properties are nil and both pragmas are empty, its equal.Kernel-ar.230:Implementations for BlockClosure>>isValid and asMinimalRepresentation for compatibility of BlockClosure with the when:evaluate: protocol.Kernel-ar.231:BlockClosure>>asMinimalRepresentation needs to return self, just like the comment says."!!BlockClosure methodsFor: 'events-support' stamp: 'ar 8/26/2009 21:36'!asMinimalRepresentation	"For use in the when:evaluate: protocol, i.e.,		foo when: #bar evaluate:[self handleBar].	Return the receiver."	^self! !!Pragma methodsFor: 'testing' stamp: 'djr 8/26/2009 22:39'!analogousCodeTo: aPragma	^ (self arguments = aPragma arguments) &		(self keyword = aPragma keyword)! !!MethodProperties methodsFor: 'testing' stamp: 'djr 8/27/2009 00:18'!analogousCodeTo: aMethodProperties	pragmas		ifNil: [aMethodProperties pragmas notEmpty ifTrue: [^false]]		ifNotNil:			[pragmas size ~= aMethodProperties pragmas size ifTrue:				[^false].			 pragmas with: aMethodProperties pragmas do:				[:mine :others|				(mine analogousCodeTo: others) ifFalse: [^false]]].	(self propertiesIsNil and: [aMethodProperties propertiesIsNil]) ifTrue: [^true].	^(self hasAtLeastTheSamePropertiesAs: aMethodProperties)	  and: [aMethodProperties hasAtLeastTheSamePropertiesAs: self]! !!MethodProperties methodsFor: 'testing' stamp: 'MagmaCollectionTester 8/26/2009 23:08'!propertiesIsNil	^ properties isNil! !!Object methodsFor: 'system primitives' stamp: 'dtl 8/29/2009 12:55'!oopString	"Answer a string that represents the oop of the receiver.	This method is for compatibility only, see comment for #asOop."	^ self asOop printString! !!MethodProperties methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'MagmaCollectionTester 8/26/2009 23:10'!keysAndValuesDo: aBlock	properties keysAndValuesDo: aBlock! !!BlockClosure methodsFor: 'events-support' stamp: 'ar 8/26/2009 20:58'!isValid	"For use in the when:evaluate: protocol, i.e.,		foo when: #bar evaluate:[self handleBar].	Return true."	^true! !Boolean class removeSelector: #ccg:generateCoerceToValueFrom:on:!SmallInteger class removeSelector: #ccg:generateCoerceToOopFrom:on:!SmallInteger class removeSelector: #ccgCanConvertFrom:!Boolean class removeSelector: #ccg:prolog:expr:index:!SmallInteger class removeSelector: #ccg:generateCoerceToValueFrom:on:!SmallInteger class removeSelector: #ccg:prolog:expr:index:!Boolean class removeSelector: #ccg:emitLoadFor:from:on:!Boolean class removeSelector: #ccg:generateCoerceToOopFrom:on:!